<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200903/0f41585b299b4faeaf0dafffc0e0d8e8.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">小学生观摩并品尝康师傅方便面</span></img></p>
